Sharing a small clip of Ae Ri Pawan, one of my favourite songs. Composed by legendary RD Burman ji and sung by Maa Saraswati Lata Mangeshkar ji. Beautifully written by Anand Bakshi ji. Hope you all enjoy listening to my rendition of the song. 😇❤️
Humble pranaam to the legends 🙇‍♀️🙏
.
.
#latamangeshkar #rdburman #liveconcert #songs #oldsongs #music #bollywoodsongs #goodmusic

Hey everyone! Hope you all are doing well. Back with a short cover of one of my favourite songs of Maa Saraswati @lata_mangeshkar ji, ‘Aap Kyun Roye’. Originally composed by the legendary Madan Mohan ji and written by great Raja Mehdi Ali Khan ji. Hope you all like my rendition of this song! ❤️✨
